    <item>
      <title>拜登任期仅剩几周 赦免儿子亨特</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/president-biden-says-he-signed-a-pardon-for-his-son-hunter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登签署了对其儿子亨特·拜登的全面赦免令，扭转了他之前不使用行政权力来帮助其长子的立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/president-biden-says-he-signed-a-pardon-for-his-son-hunter</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 00:37:47 GMT</pubDate>
